 "\nNotice how instead of going to the left and down, we go to the right and \
up. This means instead of the subtraction like in ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["p", "1"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9c1eaad7-f7a7-478a-85bc-8dbea1fb8b70"],
