  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["p", "5"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "adcf7f6e-a37d-489c-a5b5-7d1a16265292"],
 " is defined as the following:\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["p", "5"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "eec60660-8589-4e7e-9833-bac0f8b41d3a"],
