 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "lean"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "c75c291c-a3c5-491a-89b9-acd5e0c61a00"],
 "),",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["d", "tail"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d37111dc-244a-4057-ad6a-2e99d46a3dcc"],
 "*sin(",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "lean"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "1ec97e5c-a59e-43b2-8ca0-f0eedbb821ca"],
 "))\n\nWe can then define it in Wolfram Language using this line of code:"
}], "Text",
